    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_4_1005-1047",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1005-1047",
      "markText": "丘吉尔、希特勒、墨索里尼和罗斯福，他们作为军事领袖都是可以替代的，唯独斯大林不可以。",
      "totalCount": 130,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1005&rangeEnd=1047",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1005&rangeEnd=1047"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_437-509",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "437-509",
      "markText": "在20世纪的独裁者当中，约瑟夫·斯大林(Joseph Stalin)的残忍与有罪的名声，只有阿道夫·希特勒(Adolf Hitler)可与之相比",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=437&rangeEnd=509",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=437&rangeEnd=509"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_10574-10605",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "10574-10605",
      "markText": "对有争议的1939～1941年的《苏德互不侵犯条约》进行了批评",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10574&rangeEnd=10605",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10574&rangeEnd=10605"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_11_6945-7016",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "6945-7016",
      "markText": "斯大林一定是这样想的：如果希特勒铁了心要开战，他肯定就让他的日本盟友不要与苏联签订条约。日本愿意签订中立条约，不仅是东京也是柏林发出的积极信号",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6945&rangeEnd=7016",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6945&rangeEnd=7016"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_33413-33482",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "33413-33482",
      "markText": "后一种解读往往与对斯大林的如下看法联系在一起——这种看法强调，他是个空想家，一个真正信仰共产主义的人，他对自己有关阶级敌人的宣传信以为真了",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=33413&rangeEnd=33482",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=33413&rangeEnd=33482"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_36095-36130",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "36095-36130",
      "markText": "生活在苏联边境地区的许多族群都被认为是那种一旦发生战争就可能背叛的人。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=36095&rangeEnd=36130",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=36095&rangeEnd=36130"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_11959-11997",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "11959-11997",
      "markText": "有关斯大林与希特勒的条约的争议，根本上是关于这一邪恶同盟的成本与收益的争论。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11959&rangeEnd=11997",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11959&rangeEnd=11997"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_20466-20516",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "20466-20516",
      "markText": "对斯大林的另外一些指责是：对前线军事行动的过度干预、在危急关头失去镇定以及把别人当作自己错误的替罪羊",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=20466&rangeEnd=20516",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=20466&rangeEnd=20516"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_37332-37359",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "37332-37359",
      "markText": "害怕民族主义的分离主义在战争中可能对苏联的生存构成威胁",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=37332&rangeEnd=37359",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=37332&rangeEnd=37359"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_21_20283-20346",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "20283-20346",
      "markText": "但是，无论是斯大林还是罗斯福都没有预见到在这方面会遇到大的困难，他们两人都以为中国人会对苏联参战千恩万谢，任何交易都不成问题。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=20283&rangeEnd=20346",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=20283&rangeEnd=20346"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_20918-20948",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "20918-20948",
      "markText": "例如，苏军的伤亡人数达到了16000万，其中阵亡达800万。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=20918&rangeEnd=20948",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=20918&rangeEnd=20948"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_12737-12773",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "12737-12773",
      "markText": "苏联之所以会在一开始受到挫折，主要是因为红军的部署是着眼于进攻而不是防御",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12737&rangeEnd=12773",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12737&rangeEnd=12773"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_39991-40033",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "39991-40033",
      "markText": "列宁和斯大林相信工人阶级超越并战胜国家界限的团结，他们在原则上都反对民族主义的排外性",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=39991&rangeEnd=40033",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=39991&rangeEnd=40033"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_14_35624-35724",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "35624-35724",
      "markText": "当艾登表示那就是指“莫洛托夫—里宾特洛甫线”时，斯大林说，他怎么叫它都行。莫洛托夫插话说，他们现在都称它“寇松线”，而在英国外交大臣寇松勋爵所确定的人种界线与苏联人提出的苏波边界线之间，并没有多少区别",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=35624&rangeEnd=35724",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=35624&rangeEnd=35724"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_49256-49336",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "49256-49336",
      "markText": "且共产党中国的不情愿的介入才使得他的政权免遭灭顶之灾。这使得斯大林与中国领导人毛泽东之间的关系开始恶化，而这场战争本身最终在军事、政治和经济上的代价也是极高的。",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=49256&rangeEnd=49336",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=49256&rangeEnd=49336"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_25_34454-34509",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "34454-34509",
      "markText": "已经两年了，美国还是不能征服小小的朝鲜……他们想要征服世界，却连小小的朝鲜也征服不了。这些美国人打仗真是不行。",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=34454&rangeEnd=34509",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=34454&rangeEnd=34509"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_6216-6241",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6216-6241",
      "markText": "他认为斯大林使用了野蛮的手段来消除苏联的落后与野蛮",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6216&rangeEnd=6241",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6216&rangeEnd=6241"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_9_10963-11016",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "10963-11016",
      "markText": "斯大林之所以与希特勒签订条约，是为了扭转局势，让西方诸强自食其果，从而使自己在即将到来的战争中有腾挪的空间",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071745&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10963&rangeEnd=11016",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44032500813ab8286g01559f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10963&rangeEnd=11016"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071745_12_1090-1161",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1090-1161",
      "markText": "要防止还有战斗力的人员撤退到辽阔的苏联内地……行动的最终目标是要建立一条大致沿伏尔加河到阿尔汉格尔斯克(Arkhangel)的防御苏联的屏障。",
      "totalCount": 64,
